iKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Quy-t%E1%BB%B1-dao-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-2d1A1bSdRHHa9EueuPLyTg">Quy tự dao kỳ 3 - 歸字謠其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-77k7d_i26Q3zI_gu_1iz-w">Trương Hiếu Tường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-12/poem-2ZPU_-ZZ0CV7HttrnRftSA">Trúc chi từ kỳ 12 - 竹枝詞其十二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/author-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Vương Quang Duẫn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-Ph%C3%A0n-%C3%94-K%E1%BB%B3/poem-CWqmV1oA-0z3PPzA4fhnPQ">Vịnh sử - Phàn Ô Kỳ - 詠史－樊於期</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/author-U-Qw0U7nLVKqm8kibmDN6g">Hà Ngô Sô</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A2y-m%C3%B4n-kh%E1%BA%A9u-chi%E1%BA%BFm/poem-GFMdax1vpYhdyMW3NDE5fw">Xuất tây môn khẩu chiếm - 出西北門口占</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
